ReportBundle.ReportXML: <Report ReportGID="feeba34b-d47c-443a-9525-a7fa2753af38" ReportUseType="2" ReportType="5" ReportName="Ingredient Usage by Pen Type" CreatedDT="2012-11-08T13:43:17" ModifiedDT="2014-05-19T10:33:33.303" ModifiedBy="VAS" ConcurrencyTS="AAAAAAAAJyk=" ReportVersion="1" />

ReportQuery.ReportQueryText: <QueryBundle> <QueryText>select z.* from ( select pen_types.PrimaryPenTypeName ,cmp.CompanyName ,hii.InventoryItemName as 'IngredientName' ,hpn.PenNumber ,htl.LocationName as 'LocationName' ,PenName = case when htl.LocationType = 1 then htl.LocationName else null end ,fs.InstanceDate as 'ReportDate' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'AF Qty' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, cmp.LargeMeasurementType) as 'AF Tons' ,it.DMPct * dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'DM Qty' ,it.DMPct * dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, cmp.LargeMeasurementType) as 'DM Tons' ,it.DMPct from InventoryTransaction it with (nolock) left join Pen pn with (nolock) on pn.LocationGID = it.ToLocationGID left join HistoryPen hpn with (nolock) on hpn.HistoryPenGID = (select top 1 HistoryPenGID from HistoryPen where HistoryPen.PenGID = pn.PenGID and HistoryPen.CreatedDT <= DATEADD(SECOND, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT) order by HistoryPen.CreatedDT desc) join HistoryLocation htl with (nolock) on htl.HistoryLocationGID = it.ToHistoryLocationGID join Location tl with (nolock) on tl.LocationGID = it.ToLocationGID join Company cmp with (nolock) on cmp.CompanyGID = tl.CompanyGID join HistoryInventoryItem hii with (nolock) on hii.HistoryInventoryItemGID = it.HistoryInventoryItemGID join FeedingScheduleDrop fsd with (nolock) on fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID = it.TransactionSourceGID join FeedingScheduleLoad fsl with (nolock) on fsl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID join FeedingScheduleMix fsm with (nolock) on fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsl.FeedingScheduleMixGID join FeedingSchedule fs with (nolock) on fs.FeedingScheduleGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleGID cross apply ( select pt.PrimaryPenTypeName from dbo.GetPenTypes(pn.PenGID, dateadd(second, -it.durationseconds, it.transactiondt)) pt ) pen_types ) z where (1=1)</QueryText> <PreQueryText /> </QueryBundle>
